we've been talking about?

03:01.081 --> 03:02.750
Ohh, Dylan and I
have plans.

03:02.783 --> 03:04.752
We're picking up some stuff
for JJ's man cave.

03:04.785 --> 03:05.786
Maybe when I get back?

03:05.819 --> 03:07.421
I can come with.
Dylan won't mind.

03:07.455 --> 03:08.456
Wow.

03:08.489 --> 03:09.990
You have been gone
a long time.

03:10.023 --> 03:11.759
