03:19.267 --> 03:21.802
"That's his --" D-A --
"dating app.

03:21.835 --> 03:23.404
Someone matched with him."

03:23.437 --> 03:25.706
Ooh!
Let's see this lucky lady.

03:25.739 --> 03:28.108
Run!
Give me that!

03:28.141 --> 03:30.278
Save yourself!

03:30.311 --> 03:31.379
All right, let's see.

03:31.412 --> 03:32.480
Uh...

03:32.513 --> 03:33.581
Huh!

03:33.614 --> 03:35.816
